        "subject": "LU-1606 api: Define empty LASSERT (and variants) for user space",
        "message": "LU-1606 api: Define empty LASSERT (and variants) for user space\n\nWe need to have SOME definition of LASSERT and its variants\nfor user space, because they have crept into places like\nlustre_idl.h.  Since a library intended to be used by normal\nusers should not be triggering assertiions in the first place,\nit seems somewhat reasonable to make these no-ops.\n\nChange-Id: I844eb045586a742544100265937639e52ce739eb\nSigned-off-by: Christopher J. Morrone <morrone2@llnl.gov>\n"
      },
